com.github.seqware.queryengine.factory
Class SWQEFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.factory.SWQEFactory

public class SWQEFactory
extends Object

This is the SeqWare Query Engine factory and should be used as the primary entry-point for developers. Only go "behind" to access serialization or back-ends directly if you want to work on implementation-specific classes.
